---
import ThemeLayout from '../layouts/ThemeLayout.astro';
---
<ThemeLayout page="services" heading="B2B Development Services">

  <section class="inner-page padd-section">
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row align-items-center mb-5" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-12 text-center mb-4 mb-md-0">
          <div class="svc-hero-icon">
            <i class="fa fa-handshake-o"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-10">
          <h3>Business-to-Business Web Development</h3>
          <p>One of the most in-demand services for organizations worldwide, B2B development from Rayinfos Technologies helps improve efficiency, attract global customers and grow your digital presence. Using the latest technologies — PHP, XML and JavaScript — we deliver custom portal solutions that match your business criteria exactly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-globe"></i></div>
            <h5>Global Reach</h5>
            <p>Expand your customer base with B2B portals that attract international clients and increase awareness of your business in the online market.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-code"></i></div>
            <h5>Modern Technologies</h5>
            <p>Solutions built on PHP, XML and JavaScript using the latest proven technologies, including document and content management systems and hosting services.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-sitemap"></i></div>
            <h5>Portal Development</h5>
            <p>Custom B2B portal development services that are exceptional in creating websites according to the exact criteria provided by you.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-file-text-o"></i></div>
            <h5>Document Management</h5>
            <p>Integrated document and content management systems that streamline your business workflow and information management end-to-end.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-money"></i></div>
            <h5>Cost Reduction</h5>
            <p>Lowered overhead and management costs with reduced customer acquisition costs — improving business productivity while cutting overall expenses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
          <div class="svc-card">
            <div class="svc-card-icon"><i class="fa fa-users"></i></div>
            <h5>Customer Relations</h5>
            <p>Better customer care facilities, longer-lasting business relationships and availability of larger community participation through a bigger platform.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</ThemeLayout>
